API Methods:
-----------

GET --> fetch the data
POST --> create a record/update the record
PUT --> update the record
DELETE --> delete the record

API Status Code:

200, 201 --> Success
400,401,404 --> Failure (Resource not found)


json query

##########################################################
Invoke-WebRequest www.google.com -UseBasicParsing 

Invoke-RestMethod -Uri "https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts" -Method Get

$result = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get -Uri "https://api.restful-api.dev/objects"  -Credential $cred 

$result | Where-Object {$_.id -eq 1} | select name


